al approach to cardiac tamponade</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">J.R. Fortuño Andrés</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">A. Alguersuari Cabiscol</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">J. Falcó Fages</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">E. Castañer González</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">P. Bermudez Bencerrey</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2010Jan1 | Radiología (English Edition), Vol. 52, No. 5</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S2173-5107(10)70030-6">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1016/j.jcct.2010.01.004"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jcct.2010.01.004">Computed tomography of the pericardium and pericardial disease</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Prabhakar Rajiah</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">Jeffrey P. Kanne</span></li></ul></div><div class="meta">2010Jan1 | Journal of Cardiovascular Computed Tomography, Vol. 4, No. 1</div></div><div class="getFTR external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jcct.2010.01.004">Crossref</a></div></div></li><li class="citedByEntry" data-doi="10.1016/j.crad.2009.09.002"><div class="related"><div class="related__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.crad.2009.09.002">MRI and CT appearances of cardiac tumours in adults</a></div><div class="related__authors"><ul class="rlist--inline loa mobile-authors loa-height"><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">E.T.D. Hoey</span><span>, </span></li><li><span class="hlFld-ContribAuthor">K. Mankad</span><span>, </